objects.description: [IcedID](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0483) can inject itself into a suspended msiexec.exe process to send beacons to C2 while appearing as a normal msi application. (Citation: Juniper IcedID June 2020) [IcedID](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0483) has also used msiexec.exe to deploy the [IcedID](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0483) loader.(Citation: Trendmicro_IcedID)
